headline: Chinese researchers find bat virus enters human cells via same pathway as COVID
summary: A newly discovered bat coronavirus uses the same cell-surface protein to gain entry into human cells as the SARS-CoV-2 virus that causes COVID-19, raising the possibility that it could someday spread...
